data.description: REDUCED...and Move-In Ready...just add your personal touch. 3 bedroom-2 bath in-law plan home in Steeplechase.  Check out the upgraded Range.  Painted and installed LVP (luxury vinyl plank) flooring 2023. Features gas logs fireplace, bay window in kitchen eating area, oversized back patio with cover, Nicely landscaped yard with Sprinkler System and privacy fenced backyard with tool shed, Primary Bath with Garden tub/shower and dual sinks, all Kitchen appliances stay...even the refrigerator, house water softener included too. Solar driven roof vent fan to keep the heat out of the attic. 2-car garage. Walk to Fuentes Elementary. Close to IDEA School, HEB, Walmart and Ascension Seton Hays Hospital. This house is ready for you to make it yours.
